
##Warning###

[Requires]
1. ImageMagick & Jmagick
	See : http://www.jmagick.org
	And download...
			Image Magick
				ImageMagick-6.3.9-0-Q16-windows-dll.exe for windows
				or 
				ImageMagick-i686-pc-linux-gnu.tar.gz for linux
			
			JMagick
				jmagick-win-6.3.9-Q16.zip

2. Tomcat

[Parameters]

height : height of resized image
width : width of resized image
path : image path (Http or file)
quality : 0 - 100

e.g.
http://localhost:8080/img?height=600&width=600&path=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.travelnow.com%2Fhotels%2F2000000%2F1700000%2F1699500%2F1699407%2F1699407_61_b.jpg&quality=10


[Note]
Recommend you to use mod_cache and mod_proxy.

Example settings.

	<IfModule mod_proxy.c>
		<IfModule mod_proxy_ajp.c>
			Include "conf/extra/httpd-ajp.conf"
		</IfModule>
		ProxyPass /images http://images.travelnow.com
		ProxyPassReverse /images http://images.travelnow.com
	</IfModule>
	
	<IfModule mod_cache.c>
		Header set Expires "Thu, 01 Jan 2099 00:00:00 GMT"
		CacheIgnoreCacheControl On
		CacheIgnoreNoLastMod On
		CacheMaxExpire 604800
		<IfModule mod_disk_cache.c>
			CacheRoot c:/temp/cache
			CacheEnable disk /
			CacheDirLevels 6
			CacheDirLength 3
		</IfModule>
	</IfModule>
	
	
